				PRINTFORMW 「You never know when one might be listening～」

			CASE 37
				PRINTFORML 「I really wish people would stop calling spiders bugs.」
				CALL PRINT_STRW, @"「They're not bugs! They're arachnids! They @ITALIC@eat@ bugs!」"
				PRINTFORMDW Wriggle swallows.
				PRINTFORML 「It's why I'm always nervous around Yamame-san.」
				PRINTFORMW 「%HE_SHE([[ヤマメ]],1)%'s friendly enough, but sometimes %HE_SHE([[ヤマメ]])% just gets this hungry look in %HIS_HER([[ヤマメ]])% eyes...」

			CASE 38
