				PRINTFORMDW Wriggle sighs.
				PRINTFORMW 「I even made a bunch of badges for Bug Battlers to give to people who beat them...」

			CASE 39
				PRINTFORMW 「Have you ever been to Misty's food cart?」
				PRINTFORMW 「%HIS_HER([[ミスティア]],1)% food is delicious! I never knew eels could taste so good...」
				PRINTFORMW 「And you should definitely try the Fried Cicada Sloughs. They're great, I promise!」

			CASE 40
				PRINTFORMW %BREAKENG(@"「A couple years ago, the Three Fairies of Light told me they were holding a New Year's Day festival at the Hakurei Shrine.」")%
				PRINTFORMW %BREAKENG(@"「I decided to open an Insect Relief stall there. It was pretty successful, so I figured I'd offer it as a full-time service.」")%
				PRINTFORMW 「So if you're having problems with insects showing up where they aren't wanted, just leave it to me!」
				PRINTFORMW 「I'll find 'em and tell 'em to... buzz off!」
				PRINTFORMDW Wriggle snickers to %HIM_HER([[リグル]])%self.
				PRINTFORMDW When %HE_SHE([[リグル]])% notices you aren't laughing, %HE_SHE([[リグル]])% looks a little offended.
				PRINTFORMW 「What? C'mon, it was kinda funny...」
				PRINTFORMDW Wriggle folds %HIS_HER([[リグル]])% arms and sulks.

