						PRINTFORMW 「Wow... bees really are smart!」
						PRINTFORMW 「And so are you, if you know cool stuff like that!」
						PRINTFORMDW Wriggle smiles at you.
						PRINTFORMDL
						PRINTFORMDL Favor +100 (Wriggle)
						PRINTFORMW
						CALL CHANGE_CFLAG(GETNUM(CFLAG, "好感度"), [[リグル]], 100)
