				PRINTFORMW 「I can never find anyone to play with.」
				PRINTFORML 「%CHAN_KUN([[ルーミア]])% and %CHAN_KUN([[チルノ]])% can't remember the rules, Misty can't hold the ball because of %HIS_HER([[ミスティア]])% claws...」
				PRINTFORMW %BREAKENG(@"「And the one time Mokou-san agreed to play with me, Kaguya-san showed up in the middle of the game and they started fighting.」")%

