				PRINTFORML 「"Whenever I try to remember what happened before I put this ribbon on, my head gets all fuzzy."」
				PRINTFORMW 「"But you and your bug friends always forget stuff that's not important, right? So my ribbon must not be important either!"」
				PRINTFORMDW Wriggle frowns.
				PRINTFORMW 「I dunno... I think there's something special about that ribbon.」
				PRINTFORMW 「I wish I was smart enough to figure it out...」


			CASE 46
				SIF !TALENT:[[リグル]]:恋人
					GOTO REGULAR_CONVOS
				PRINTFORMDW Wriggle is wearing a flower crown.
				PRINTFORMW 「It's cute, isn't it? Rumia-chan made it for me.」
				PRINTFORMW 「She made you one, too!」
				PRINTFORMDW She blushes.
				PRINTFORM 「She said 
				IF IS_MALE(MASTER)
					IF IS_MALE([[リグル]])
