		PRINTFORML 「And then I'd give myself a new name. A name just as cool as I am. I'd call myself...」
		PRINTFORMDW Wriggle strikes a pose.
		PRINTFORMW 「Super Wriggle!」
		PRINTFORMDW You stare blankly at her.
		PRINTFORML 「Okay, maybe the name needs some work. How about...」
		PRINTFORMW 「Super Duper Wriggle!」
